<title>tẖqty fy sẖkẖṣk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (tẖqty fy sẖkẖṣk ḥqyqẗ .. btqwĩy ạ̹ymạny
 yạlly ạ̹nt ḥy btṣnʿ .. ạlkẖyr ʿlsẖạny)2
 ạlqrạr- (mạ hw ạ̹nt ạlly kẖạlqny .. wṣạnʿny wnạsẖỷny)2
 wdʿwtny bạsmy .. (wlạ ywm btnsạny)2
 2- (ʿạrf fkry wṭryqy .. wạlạ̉nãh fy ḍlwʿy
 kạsẖf ḍʿfy ạlḥqyqy .. yạ rby yạ yswʿy)2</lyrics>
